sub_title: Senior director at Philips Foundation Impact Investments BV and Philips Foundation
summary: Leadership focused on sustainable results. Down-to-earth and decisive, quickly penetrates to the core. Can bring organizations to the next stage. Motivates people behind business goals. Figurehead function, stakeholder-sensitive, visionary, inspiring and result-driven. Expert where business meets society and transformation processes. Passion for a sustainable future; technology; people; and the bigger picture.
